      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王十朋上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "破阵子引",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "昨夜东风蓦吹透，报道桃花逐水流。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同破阵子引",
      "speakers": [
        "王母",
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "新愁惹旧愁。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "母亲拜揖。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "罢了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "极目家乡远，白云天际头。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "五年离故里，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李成上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "洒泪湿征裘。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "告母亲知道。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "起来说。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "是。孩儿昨夜，梦见媳妇，扯住孩儿衣袂，说道十朋吓，十朋，我只与你同忧，不与你同乐。醒来却是南柯一梦。",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "敢是媳妇与你讨祭了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿祭礼已备，请母亲主祭。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "吓！啊呀媳妇儿吓！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "非是儿夫负你情，只因奸相妒良姻。生前淑性甘贞洁，死后阴魂脱世尘。餐玉馔，饮瑶樽，水晶宫里伴仙人。待你儿夫任满朝金阙，与你伸冤奏紫宸。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "儿吓，你去祭罢。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "是，孩儿告祭了。吓！啊呀妻吓！我与你好似巫山一片云，秦岭一堆雪，阆苑一枝花，瑶台一轮月。到如今，云散雪消，花残月缺，好不伤感人也！",
      "text_length": 65
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "新水令",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "一从科第凤鸾飞，被奸谋有书空寂。幸萱堂无祸危，痛兰房受岑寂，捱不过凌逼。啊呀妻吓！恁身沉在浪涛里！",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "咳！（步步娇）将往事今朝重提起，",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
