    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "折桂令",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "越恼得肝肠碎。清明祭扫时，省却愁烦，且自酬醴。李舅看酒。有酒。卑幼之丧，何劳母亲奠酒？儿吓！须记得圣贤书道，我不与祭如不祭。李舅看香！有。爇沉檀香喷金猊，昭告灵魂，听剖因依。自从俺宴罢瑶池，宫袍宠赐，相府把俺勒赘，俺只为撇不下糟糠𠮾旧妻，苦推辞桃杏新室。致受磨折，改调俺在潮阳，啊呀妻吓！因此上耽误了恁的归期。",
      "text_length": 155
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "江儿水",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "听说罢衷肠事，只为伊，却原来不从招赘生奸计。懊恨娘行忒薄义，凌逼得你好没存济。母子虔诚遥祭，望鉴微忱，早赐灵魂来至。",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00032",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "李舅看酒。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00033",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李成"
      ],
      "text": "有酒。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00034",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "雁儿落带得胜令",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "徒捧着泪盈盈一酒巵，空列着香馥馥八珍味，慕音容不见伊，诉衷曲无回对。呀！俺这里再拜自追思，重会面是何时？揾不住双垂泪，舒不开咱两道眉。先室！𠲔！恨只恨套书信的贼施计。贤妻！俺若是昧诚心自有天鉴知！啊呀，昧诚心自有天鉴知！",
      "text_length": 110
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00035",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "侥侥令",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "不是爹行没主意，是你继母太心欺，贪恋富室豪门财和礼，抛闪得好夫妻中路里，好夫妻中路里。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00036",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "收江南",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "呀！早知道这般样拆散呵，谁待要赴春闱？便做到腰金衣紫待何如？说来的话儿，又恐怕外人知端的，倒不如布衣，布衣，啊呀妻吓！只索要低声啼哭自伤悲！",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00037",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "园林好",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "免愁烦回辞了奠仪。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00038",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀媳妇儿吓！我本待要拜你一拜，恐你消受不起。罢！",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00039",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "园林好",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "只得拜冯夷，多加些护持。早早向波心脱离，惟愿取免沉溺，惟愿取免沉溺。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00040",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "李舅化纸。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00041",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李成"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00042",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "沽美酒",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "纸钱飘，蝴蝶飞，纸钱飘，蝴蝶飞。血泪染，杜鹃啼，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00043",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "儿吓，将媳妇绣鞋也焚了罢。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00044",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "沽美酒",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "睹物伤情越惨凄。灵魂儿恁自知，俺不是负心的，负心的随着灯灭，花谢有芳菲时节，月缺有团圆之夜。俺呵，徒然间早起晚息，想伊家念伊。啊呀妻吓！要相逢除非是梦儿里，和你再成姻契。",
      "text_length": 85
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00045",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "王母",
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "昏昏默默归何处？哽哽咽咽常念你，",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00046",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李成下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00047",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "王母",
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "直上嫦娥宫殿里。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00048",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "年年此日须当祭，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00049",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "岁岁今朝不可迟。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00050",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "天长地久有时尽，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00051",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "此恨绵绵无绝期。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00052",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王母"
      ],
      "text": "随我进来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00053",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王十朋"
      ],
      "text": "是。啊呀妻吓！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902105_e00054",
      "play_id": "70902105",
      "scene_id": "70902105_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王母、王十朋同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    }
